event.title: Monthly Fellowship meeting in Vienna, Austria
event.body: This month, the Vienna Fellowship meeting will be in the Metalab, located in the Rathausstra√üe 6 in the 1st district of Vienna. We'll be there from 18:00, with agenda related discussions starting at 19:00. As usual, this invitation is for everyone interested in the FSFE or Free Software. We're looking forward to seeing you there!
